						<summary>

						<p>Fragmentary. Seems to record a gift of land at Āppikkūḍal for offerings to god Eḍuttakai-Aḻagiya-Nāyaṉār. The record is dated in the <hi rend="bold">5th year of Perumāḷ Vīra-Kulaśēkharadēva.</hi> It is engraved in characters of about the 15th century. In the absence of other details it is not possible to identify the king. </p>						

						</summary>
